                            <comment id="14438194" author="joerg.hohwiller@sdm.de" created="Wed, 11 Apr 2007 06:01:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tried the official 2.1. The bug still remains. Simply try &quot;mvn site:stage -DstagingDirectory=/absolute/path/...&quot; on a project with javadoc and jxr.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
